NetworkManager: NetworkManager (NetworkManager for Pain-Free Networking)
NetworkManager:
NetworkManager: NetworkManager attempts to make networking invisible. When moving 
NetworkManager: into areas you've been before, NetworkManager automatically connects 
NetworkManager: to the last network the user chose to connect to. Likewise, when 
NetworkManager: back at the desk, NetworkManager will switch to the faster, more 
NetworkManager: reliable wired network connection. 
